If a user is on the "Add Page" or "Add News" pages and choose to click on "Cancel", they are not brought back to the page from where this action was originally initiated, but are instead brought to the "Pages - Alphabetical View" page.
This should be changed to bring them back to the previous page that they were on, if "Cancel" is clicked.

