When selecting one of the sample profile pictures, the CSS high-lighting works so that the radio button highlights when I hover over a profile pic (e.g., the devil).  But I have to actually click the radio button to select the picture.

Minor usability, but I'd love to just be able to click the picture itself, rather than using radio buttons. They're so Web 1.0.  (haha)

