The calendar plugin is useful, but I'd like a way to prevent the weekend days from being displayed.  Alternatively, I'd like a way when creating events that span multiple days to specify weekdays only.    Right now, if I have an event that spans more than one week, I either have to create separate events for each week or see a distracting inaccruate view which shows the event as spanning across the weekends.
